title: Migos - Back to the Bando
description:
Migos are "Back to the Bando" with a fire new tape.

Less than 2 months after dropping their debut album, Yung Rich Nation, Migos are back with a new mixtape, Back to the Bando. As you can tell by the title, the trio of Quavo, Offset, and Takeoff are back in the trap house and have brought the same feel that gave us classics like No Label and Rich Nigga Timeline. 

The 15-track release doesn't have any features, but we've got more than enough energy from the young Migos, and the production here is absolutely master-class, featuring Deko, Dun Deal, Murda Beatz, and 7 beats from the Almighty Zaytoven. 

Download Back to the Bando, and watch the brand new video to the Dun-Deal produced "Trap Problems" below.
